Enter your .py or any other relavant files inside this project code folder.

Instructions for uploading files (2 ways):
1.Access Upload Tool: Inside your repository, click the "Add file" button and select "Upload files" from the GitHub Web Interface.
2.Drag and Drop: Drag your files or folders from your computer into the browser box.

* Commit Changes: At the bottom, type a short message (e.g., "Initial upload") and click "Commit changes" to save them to the repository. 
